The paper deals with the modeling and performance analysis of 3D Massive MIMO systems, which involves information theory, networking, systems and control, multimedia, and computer communication networks. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.COM (Computer Communication Networks).
